microprocessor_definition.name: Simple Generator Controller
microprocessor_definition.description: Controls the essential Parts of an advanced generator

object.script:
s=screen function onTick() battery=input.getNumber(1) connected=input.getBool(1) end
function onDraw() s.setColor(155,155,155) s.drawRectF(0,0,32,32) s.setColor(0,0,0) s.drawText(1,2,"Charge") if connected==false then s.setColor(0,80,0) s.drawText(5,10,"idle") else s.setColor(10,10,10) s.drawRect(3,11,9,19) s.drawRectF(4,10,8,1) s.setColor(0,80,0) s.drawRectF(4,30-19*battery,8,19*battery) s.drawText(13,12,string.format("%.0f",100*battery)) s.drawText(28,12,"%") end end
